Assignment:
1. Refactor or just create a separate registration/login tests using TestNG framework with @DataProvider.
2. Create an xml suite for your test classes.
[OPTIONAL] 3. Move logic of setting up/cleaning driver to listener.
If you want to start/stop browser before/after each test -> implement IInvokedMethodListener
                                  before/after each class-> implement IClassListener
4.Configure your xml suite to make use of the above listener
5.Create and register in the suite a listener taking screenshots on test failure. Implement ITestListener interface or extend adapter class TestListenerAdapter  and override the corresponding method
[OPTIONAL]: 6.Create a xml suite with a two <test> tests containing the same test class , set TestNG to parallel "classes" and add browser parameter to the suite so that you can run the same test classes in parallel using different browsers.
